Database schema changes are managed with Flask-Migrate/Alembic.

For a new database:

    flask --app wsgi:app db upgrade

For a pre-existing deployment that already matches the baseline schema, verify
the tables and indexes first, back up PostgreSQL, then mark the baseline once:

    flask --app wsgi:app db stamp 20260610_0001

Do not stamp a database whose schema has not been independently verified.

